==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Londonize
<hw>Lon"don*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To impart to
(one) a manner or character like that which distinguishes
Londoners.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Londonize</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Londonize
<hw>Lon"don*ize</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To imitate the manner of the
people of London.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>London smoke</ent>⟦br⟧
